Class Text

java.lang.Object
  de.nec.nle.siafu.types.Text
All Implemented Interfaces:
Publishable
public class Text
extends Object
implements Publishable

This Publishable encapsulates a String and makes it serializable (it can be flattened and blown up again) for use with Siafu.

Author:
Miquel Martin
